\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 34. D. korabensis} Kümmerle & Degen ex Jáv.,{\i  Bot. Közl.}{\b  19}: 22 (1921) ({\i D. tomentosa} auct. bulg., non Clairv.). Plant forming a dense mat; stem up to 16 cm. Basal leaves ovate-lanceolate, densely stellate-hairy; cauline leaves 1-8. Silicula ovate-lanceolate to elliptical, hairy; style 0·4-0·6(-0·9) mm. 2n = 32. •{\i  Mountains of N. part of Balkan peninsula}. Al Bu Ju.
